detailed.en: IBOX: If the number rotates 24 times, buy IBOX for RM1 to get 24 number combinations, 24 ÷ RM1 = RM0.04 per number. IBOX = ÷, 1234 = 24 combinations, 1134 = 12, 1133 = 6, 1113 = 4 If the issue persists, please provide more details or contact support for further assistance.
detailed.ms:
"IBOX
Jika Nombor Pusingan 24 kali
Beli IBOX Bayar RM1 Saja Boleh Dapat 24 Pasang Nombor
24 ÷ RM1 ＝ Rm0.04 Satu Nombor
IBOX = ÷
1234 =24 Pasang
1134 =12 Pasang
1133 =6 Pasang
1113 =4 Pasang"
detailed.cn: "IBOX：如果號碼旋轉24次，買IBOX只需付1令吉可得24組號碼，24 ÷ 1令吉 = 每組0.04令吉。IBOX = ÷，1234 = 24組，1134 = 12組，1133 = 6組，1113 = 4組"
